(41, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'room', '{\"name\":\"Luxury Hall Of Fame\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Hotel\\\\Models\\\\Room\",\"slug\":\"luxury-hall-of-fame\",\"slug_id\":\"17\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Our spacious room offers a cozy ambiance, modern amenities, and stunning city views.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(228, 228, 228);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:&quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:30px;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;outline:none !important;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:none !important;\\\">Ph\\u00f2ng Superior View N\\u00fai V\\u00e0 Th\\u00e0nh Ph\\u1ed1&nbsp;\\u2013 Kh\\u00f4ng gian ngh\\u1ec9 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng y\\u00ean b\\u00ecnh h\\u00f2a quy\\u1ec7n c\\u00f9ng thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean<\\/strong><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(228, 228, 228);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:&quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:30px;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;outline:none !important;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">S\\u1ef1 l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi cho nh\\u1eefng ai y\\u00eau th\\u00edch s\\u1ef1 y\\u00ean t\\u0129nh v\\u00e0 phong c\\u1ea3nh h\\u1eefu t\\u00ecnh. V\\u1edbi ban c\\u00f4ng ri\\u00eang r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i h\\u01b0\\u1edbng n\\u00fai C\\u00f4 Ti\\u00ean h\\u00f9ng v\\u0129, ph\\u00f2ng Superior Mountain mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian th\\u01b0 th\\u00e1i tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed1i, n\\u01a1i du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p thanh b\\u00ecnh gi\\u1eefa l\\u00f2ng ph\\u1ed1 bi\\u1ec3n Nha Trang.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(228, 228, 228);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:&quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:30px;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;outline:none !important;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:none !important;\\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec3m n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt:<\\/strong><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(228, 228, 228);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:&quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:30px;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;outline:none !important;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">- Ph\\u00f2ng r\\u1ed9ng 38m\\u00b2, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, t\\u00f4ng m\\u00e0u \\u1ea5m c\\u00f9ng n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t g\\u1ed7 \\u00f3c ch\\u00f3 sang tr\\u1ecdng<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(228, 228, 228);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:&quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-st