(159, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'room', '{\"name\":\"Pacific Double Room With Ocean View And Private Balcony Bathtub\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Hotel\\\\Models\\\\Room\",\"slug\":\"pacific-double-room-with-ocean-view-and-private-balcony-bathtub\",\"slug_id\":\"21\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"With two spacious balconies facing the vast ocean and Co Tien Mountain, Pacific Double Room With Ocean View And Private Balcony Bathtub offers a unique view and an exclusive outdoor bathtub. Perfect for soaking, sunset-watching, and creating unforgettable moments in a luxurious, poetic atmosphere.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>Pacific Double Room With Ocean View And Private Balcony Bathtub&nbsp;\\u2013 Two balconies, outdoor bathtub &amp; a romantic escape exclusive to Boton Blue<\\/p><p>With two spacious balconies facing the vast ocean and Co Tien Mountain, Pacific Double offers a unique view and an exclusive outdoor bathtub. Perfect for soaking, sunset-watching, and creating unforgettable moments in a luxurious, poetic atmosphere.<\\/p><p>Highlights:<\\/p><ul><li>44m\\u00b2, modern design with luxurious walnut furnishings<\\/li><li>2 private balconies with direct sea and mountain view<\\/li><li>King-size bed with premium spring mattress<\\/li><li>Outdoor bathtub \\u2013 exclusive Boton Blue design<\\/li><li>Low-E soundproof glass with UV protection (alpha, beta, gamma)<\\/li><li>Premium imported sanitary ware from Grohe (Europe)<\\/li><li>Top fire safety system in Nha Trang<\\/li><li>Complimentary welcome fruit, 2 bottles of water\\/day, minibar, high-speed Wifi<\\/li><li>Free access to infinity pool, gym &amp; sauna<\\/li><li>Ideal for honeymoons, anniversaries, or romantic getaways<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"order\":\"0\",\"price\":\"0\",\"number_of_rooms\":\"5\",\"number_of_beds\":\"1\",\"max_adults\":\"2\",\"max_children\":\"1\",\"size\":\"44\",\"images\":[null,\"rooms\\/pacificnct\\/1.png\",\"rooms\\/pacificnct\\/8.png\",\"rooms\\/pacificnct\\/7.png