(165, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'room', '{\"name\":\"Suite Room With Exclusive Ocean View\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Hotel\\\\Models\\\\Room\",\"slug\":\"suite-room-with-exclusive-ocean-view\",\"slug_id\":\"23\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Spanning 80m\\u00b2 with two balconies facing the sea, the Suite offers a refined, private living space. Available in Eastern and Western styles, it combines sophistication with cultural elegance for a premium experience.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p>Suite Room With Exclusive Ocean View&nbsp;\\u2013 A luxurious retreat for elite travelers<\\/p><p>Spanning 80m\\u00b2 with two balconies facing the sea, the Suite offers a refined, private living space. Available in Eastern and Western styles, it combines sophistication with cultural elegance for a premium experience.<\\/p><p>Highlights:<\\/p><ul><li>80m\\u00b2, modern design, premium walnut furnishings<\\/li><li>Two balconies with sea or city views<\\/li><li>King-size bed with Hanvico spring mattress<\\/li><li>Separate living area for maximum comfort<\\/li><li>Low-E soundproof glass, UV protection (alpha, beta, gamma)<\\/li><li>Premium imported Grohe bathroom fixtures (Europe)<\\/li><li>One of Nha Trang\\u2019s safest fire safety systems<\\/li><li>Free: welcome fruit, red wine, 2 bottles of water\\/day, minibar, Wifi<\\/li><li>Free access to infinity pool, gym &amp; sauna<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"order\":\"0\",\"price\":\"0\",\"number_of_rooms\":\"1\",\"number_of_beds\":\"2\",\"max_adults\":\"4\",\"max_children\":\"2\",\"size\":\"80\",\"images\":[null,\"rooms\\/suite\\/6e3214fb-7a23-42c5-a55f-e93400776184.jpg\",\"rooms\\/suite\\/edf22bfd-bf96-4492-a247-34e48359b539.jpg\",\"rooms\\/suite\\/ffbf8a3b-c86d-40f2-8d22-5a117da54699.jpg\",\"rooms\\/suite\\/c0ccd33a-c463-413b-9115-6f9b07c47825.jpg\",\"rooms\\/suite\\/bc9e617c-5932-4039-813f-a1c8cbcf344e.jpg\",\"rooms\\/suite\\/ac5c0d03-0c6b-483d-a747-47fc1504b4bb.jpg\",\"rooms\\/suite\\/b8aa68c3-814a-4cb3-ae98-5645f0f