(169, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'room', '{\"name\":\"Presidential Suite\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Hotel\\\\Models\\\\Room\",\"slug\":\"presidential-suite\",\"slug_id\":\"24\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Located on the 26th floor\\u2014the highest in the hotel\\u2014the Presidential Suite boasts 310m\\u00b2 of living space and 360-degree views of Nha Trang Bay, the city, and Co Tien Mountain. Designed for world leaders, elites, and those seeking absolute exclusivity.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p>Presidential Suite \\u2013 The pinnacle of luxury and elite living<\\/p><p>Located on the 26th floor\\u2014the highest in the hotel\\u2014the Presidential Suite boasts 310m\\u00b2 of living space and 360-degree views of Nha Trang Bay, the city, and Co Tien Mountain. Designed for world leaders, elites, and those seeking absolute exclusivity.<\\/p><p>Highlights:<\\/p><ul><li>310m\\u00b2 on the top floor, full 360\\u00b0 view: sea \\u2013 mountains \\u2013 city<\\/li><li>Expansive living area, private dining room, separate work &amp; lounge spaces<\\/li><li>Oversized balcony overlooking the bay and mountains<\\/li><li>King-size bed with premium spring mattress<\\/li><li>Low-E soundproof glass, UV protection (alpha, beta, gamma)<\\/li><li>Premium Grohe bathroom fixtures (Europe)<\\/li><li>Safest fire protection system in Nha Trang<\\/li><li>Complimentary: welcome fruit, wine, daily water, minibar, high-speed Wifi<\\/li><li>Free access to infinity pool, gym, and sauna<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"order\":\"0\",\"price\":\"0\",\"number_of_rooms\":\"9\",\"number_of_beds\":\"2\",\"max_adults\":\"6\",\"max_children\":\"1\",\"size\":\"310\",\"images\":[null,\"rooms\\/phong-tong-thong\\/640d6c11-a40a-4393-9ca1-994af77734db.jpg\",\"rooms\\/phong-tong-thong\\/f7a875ba-e09d-496f-a0f7-faa91a363b31.jpg\",\"rooms\\/phong-tong-thong\\/ee1c8f98-6615-44b6-b103-216f1fee9356.jpg\",\"rooms\\/phong-tong-thong\\/df3fac3c-6356-4f88-80ca-65dbab82ace7.jpg\",\"rooms\\/phong-tong-tho