(372, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA \\u2013 A PREMIER DESTINATION FOR WORLD-CLASS CULINARY EVENTS & BUSINESS CONNECTIONS\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"boton-blue-hotel-spa-a-premier-destination-for-world-class-culinary-events-business-connections\",\"slug_id\":\"16\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Recently, the Asian Restaurant (8th floor, Boton Blue Hotel & Spa) had the honor of being selected as the venue for FOOD DISCOVERY DAY \\u2013 a large-scale culinary event jointly organized by Moonmilk Nha Trang and Kewpie Vietnam. The event brought together leading names in the food, beverage, and distribution industries, with a mission to connect \\u2013 experience \\u2013 and spread value to the community.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>BOTON BLUE HOTEL &amp; SPA \\u2013 A PREMIER DESTINATION FOR WORLD-CLASS CULINARY EVENTS &amp; BUSINESS CONNECTIONS<\\/p><p>Recently, the Asian Restaurant (8th floor, Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa) had the honor of being selected as the venue for FOOD DISCOVERY DAY \\u2013 a large-scale culinary event jointly organized by Moonmilk Nha Trang and Kewpie Vietnam. The event brought together leading names in the food, beverage, and distribution industries, with a mission to connect \\u2013 experience \\u2013 and spread value to the community.<\\/p><p>As an internationally certified 5-star hotel, Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa takes pride in being a trusted choice for prestigious brands and strategic partners when it comes to hosting high-profile events. From elegant spaces and a professional planning team to top-tier 5-star services, we are committed to delivering a seamless, effective, and unforgettable event experience.<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udc49 FOOD DISCOVERY DAY was not only a bridge between businesses and consumers, but also a testament to Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa\\u2019s capability to host events that are professional \\u2013 flexible \\u2013 and upscale, making us the ideal destination for distinguished gatherings in the coastal city of Nha Trang.<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udcde For partners and businesses interested in hosting events, please message our Fanpage or contact our hotline at 0889 499 898 for the fastest consultation and support.<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4131.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4120.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4118.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4109.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4105.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4102.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4100.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4099.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4097.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4088.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4086.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/524060833-1160149692803591-321056546866203621-n-copy.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/522918020-1160148346137059-7450278003681095844-n-copy.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/522405352-1160147762803784-3114876323773976906-n-copy.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"status\":\"published\",\"image\":\"news\\/a-premier-destination-for-world\\/img-4097.jpeg\",\"tag\":null}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '171.243.63.154', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 6, 'BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA – A PREMIER DESTINATION FOR WORLD-CLASS CULINARY EVENTS & BUSINESS CONNECTIONS', 'primary', '2026-03-17 00:41:40', '2026-03-17 00:41:40'),
(373, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"KOREAN CULTURE WEEK AT BOTON BLUE: A HUB FOR INTERNATIONAL CULTURAL EXCHANGE\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"korean-culture-week-at-boton-blue-a-hub-for-international-cultural-exchange\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"\\u2728 Recently, Boton Blue Hotel & Spa was honored to successfully host a spectacular Hanbok Fashion Show featuring a group of models from Korea, as part of the Korean Culture Week. This event reaffirmed Boton Blue as an ideal venue for international cultural events.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>KOREAN CULTURE WEEK AT BOTON BLUE: A HUB FOR INTERNATIONAL CULTURAL EXCHANGE<\\/p><p>\\u2728 Recently, Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa was honored to successfully host a spectacular Hanbok Fashion Show featuring a group of models from Korea, as part of the Korean Culture Week. This event reaffirmed Boton Blue as an ideal venue for international cultural events.<\\/p><p>\\u2728 The Hanbok show was more than just a fashion performance\\u2014it served as a cultural bridge, bringing Korean heritage closer to Vietnamese audiences and international guests. With the luxurious and elegant setting of Boton Blue, the event became a memorable night of cultural fusion, where the timeless beauty of Hanbok harmonized with Vietnamese hospitality and traditions.<\\/p><p>\\u2728 The event attracted a large number of international guests staying at Boton Blue, as well as special invitees, creating a vibrant and engaging multicultural atmosphere. Once again, it proved that Boton Blue is not only highly regarded for its facilities but also for its professionalism and meticulous event organization. The hotel is always ready to cater to diverse cultural needs and high-caliber events.<\\/p><p>&nbsp;<\\/p><p>\\u2728 Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa is proud to be a trusted destination for international travelers\\u2014not only for leisure but also for hosting meaningful cultural events. We are committed to continuing to deliver exceptional and memorable experiences for every occasion.<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/z6701499429505-7da3b2b8ca9cbc14ff9620a6b072e0b7.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/gen-h-z6703863418592-a50992b5b64f7f3c4093b88b070ceaae.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/gen-h-z6703863388473-7cd19e012538d52d5ee11a13068ed0f5.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/ii2a5011.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/ii2a4993.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/ii2a4984.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/ii2a4967.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/ii2a4952.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/ii2a4945.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/ii2a4697.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"status\":\"published\",\"image\":\"news\\/korean-culture-week\\/gen-h-z6703863388473-7cd19e012538d52d5ee11a13068ed0f5.jpeg\",\"tag\":null}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '171.243.63.154', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 7, 'KOREAN CULTURE WEEK AT BOTON BLUE: A HUB FOR INTERNATIONAL CULTURAL EXCHANGE', 'info', '2026-03-17 00:51:26', '2026-03-17 00:51:26'),
(374, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"WELCOME PEGAS SURVEY GROUPS TO BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"welcome-pegas-survey-groups-to-boton-blue-hotel-spa\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Last week, Boton Blue Hotel & Spa had the honor of welcoming six sales representative groups with a total of 180 members from Khabarovsk, Ekaterinburg, Saint Petersburg, Krasnoyarsk, Novosibirsk, and Uzbekistan.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>WELCOME PEGAS SURVEY GROUPS TO BOTON BLUE HOTEL &amp; SPA<\\/p><p>Last week, Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa had the honor of welcoming six sales representative groups with a total of 180 members from Khabarovsk, Ekaterinburg, Saint Petersburg, Krasnoyarsk, Novosibirsk, and Uzbekistan.<\\/p><p>During their visit, the groups toured our accommodation facilities and experienced our 5-star dining and entertainment services, as part of the survey program organized by Pegas Touristik.<\\/p><p>We hope that this visit to Nha Trang will open up new opportunities for stronger connections, further promoting sustainable cooperation between the two countries, and contributing to the future growth of Nha Trang\\u2019s tourism industry.<\\/p><p>Let\'s look back at the memorable moments from the survey trip at Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa!<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/pegas-survey-groups\\/495162327-1295051572626945-1969187654488779265-n.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/pegas-survey-groups\\/494580975-1295051332626969-147425188068992823-n.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/pegas-survey-groups\\/495152788-1295051382626964-2839982910905508084-n.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/pegas-survey-groups\\/494901960-1295051362626966-2855075757089809303-n.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/pegas-survey-groups\\/494892103-1295051365960299-4747064069339498923-n.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/pegas-survey-groups\\/494701942-1295051305960305-3723114943976950451-n.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/pegas-survey-groups\\/494662862-1295051289293640-6330865991401484940-n.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/pegas-survey-groups\\/494549324-1295051575960278-7120899993965675536-n.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"status\":\"published\",\"image\":\"news\\/pegas-survey-groups\\/494892103-1295051365960299-4747064069339498923-n.jpeg\",\"tag\":null}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '171.243.63.154', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 8, 'WELCOME PEGAS SURVEY GROUPS TO BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA', 'info', '2026-03-17 01:02:09', '2026-03-17 01:02:09'),
(375, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"\\u203c\\ufe0f WARNING: MULTIPLE FAKE FANPAGES IMPERSONATING BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"warning-multiple-fake-fanpages-impersonating-boton-blue-hotel-spa\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"\\ud83d\\udea8 Recently, many fake Facebook fanpages have appeared, impersonating Boton Blue Hotel & Spa to post content and run ads promoting false promotional programs with the intent to scam customers and fraudulently obtain deposits via bank transfers.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>\\u203c\\ufe0f WARNING: MULTIPLE FAKE FANPAGES IMPERSONATING BOTON BLUE HOTEL &amp; SPA<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udea8 Recently, many fake Facebook fanpages have appeared, impersonating Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa to post content and run ads promoting false promotional programs with the intent to scam customers and fraudulently obtain deposits via bank transfers.<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udea8 We would like to inform our valued customers that Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa has only ONLY OFFICIAL FANPAGE on Facebook, accessible via the following link:<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udc49 https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/BotonBlueHotelandSpa<\\/p><p>Please exercise caution when making any payments. Kindly note that you should ABSOLUTELY NOT transfer money to any personal bank accounts.<\\/p><p>\\u26a0 Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa uses ONLY ONE official bank account for transactions, as detailed below:<\\/p><p>Account Name: C\\u00d4NG TY TNHH KINH DOANH XU\\u1ea4T NH\\u1eacP KH\\u1ea8U VI\\u1ec6T D\\u01af\\u01a0NG<\\/p><p>Bank Name: Military Commercial Joint Stock Bank (MB Bank), Khanh Hoa Branch<\\/p><p>Account Number: 8011100183006 (VND)<\\/p><p>\\u26a0 To protect your rights and ensure a safe experience, please only follow and contact us through our official channels listed below: \\ud83d\\udccc Official Fanpage: https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/BotonBlueHotelandSpa<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Official Website: https:\\/\\/botonblue.com<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Official Zalo OA: https:\\/\\/zalo.me\\/1908735166873881562<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Hotel Hotline: 0258 3836 868<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Sales Department Hotline: 0889 499 898<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc F&amp;B Department Hotline: 0889 559 090<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Hotel Email: info@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Sales Department Emails:<\\/p><p>reservation@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>sales@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>sales2@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>sales3@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>\\u26a0 All communications and promotional programs are only published on our official channels. We are not responsible for any transactions or misinformation from fake fanpages.<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udcde To verify any information, please contact us directly via our official Zalo OA, or visit our official website at www.botonblue.com and use the hotlines listed there. Our staff is always ready to assist with verification and ensure fast and secure booking. If needed, customers may request a Zalo video call to verify booking details directly.<\\/p><p>If you spot any suspicious fanpages, please report them to us promptly so we can take appropriate action.<\\/p><p>&nbsp;<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\ude4f Thank you very much for your trust and continued support!<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/warning-multiple-fake-fanpages\\/sdsd.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/warning-multiple-fake-fanpages\\/artboard-1-copy.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/warning-multiple-fake-fanpages\\/artboard-1-1.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/warning-multiple-fake-fanpages\\/493572901-1287675170031252-3014076182600375458-n.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"status\":\"published\",\"image\":\"news\\/warning-multiple-fake-fanpages\\/493572901-1287675170031252-3014076182600375458-n.jpeg\",\"tag\":null}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '171.243.63.154', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 9, '‼️ WARNING: MULTIPLE FAKE FANPAGES IMPERSONATING BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA', 'info', '2026-03-17 01:56:12', '2026-03-17 01:56:12'),
(376, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"RUSSIAN COMMUNITY FOOTBALL AWARDS GALA \\u2013 A JOURNEY OF CONNECTION AT TITAN SKY LOUNGE\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"russian-community-football-awards-gala-a-journey-of-connection-at-titan-sky-lounge\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"This past Sunday, Titan Sky Lounge \\u2013 located on the 27th floor of Boton Blue Hotel \\u2013 was honored to host the awards gala for the international community football tournament in Nha Trang. The event was not only a celebration of outstanding football teams but also an opportunity for connection, cultural exchange, and the promotion of a strong sporting spirit.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>RUSSIAN COMMUNITY FOOTBALL AWARDS GALA \\u2013 A JOURNEY OF CONNECTION AT TITAN SKY LOUNGE<\\/p><p>This past Sunday, Titan Sky Lounge \\u2013 located on the 27th floor of Boton Blue Hotel \\u2013 was honored to host the awards gala for the international community football tournament in Nha Trang. The event was not only a celebration of outstanding football teams but also an opportunity for connection, cultural exchange, and the promotion of a strong sporting spirit.<\\/p><p>Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa is proud to be a sponsor and long-term companion of the tournament, helping to create a meaningful playground for the foreign community living in Nha Trang.<\\/p><p>We would like to extend our heartfelt thanks to the organizers for choosing Titan Sky Lounge as the award ceremony venue for this special event. We hope Titan Sky Lounge will become a familiar destination for the international community in Nha Trang for future sports, cultural, and community exchange events!<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/russian-community-football\\/dsc02634-optimized.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/russian-community-football\\/dsc02629-optimized.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/russian-community-football\\/dsc02559-optimized.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/russian-community-football\\/dsc02358-optimized.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/russian-community-football\\/dsc02325-optimized.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/russian-community-football\\/dsc00977-optimized.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/russian-community-football\\/dsc00897-optimized.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/russian-community-football\\/dsc00455-optimized.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"status\":\"published\",\"image\":\"news\\/russian-community-football\\/dsc02358-optimized.jpeg\",\"tag\":null}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '171.243.63.154', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 10, 'RUSSIAN COMMUNITY FOOTBALL AWARDS GALA – A JOURNEY OF CONNECTION AT TITAN SKY LOUNGE', 'info', '2026-03-17 02:00:20', '2026-03-17 02:00:20'),
(377, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"WARNING: FAKE FANPAGES IMPERSONATING BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"warning-fake-fanpages-impersonating-boton-blue-hotel-spa\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Recently, several fake fanpages have appeared on Facebook, impersonating Boton Blue Hotel & Spa to post content and run advertisements for promotional programs with the intention of scamming and stealing customers\' money through fraudulent deposit transfers.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>\\u26a0\\ufe0f WARNING: FAKE FANPAGES IMPERSONATING BOTON BLUE HOTEL &amp; SPA<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udea8 Recently, several fake fanpages have appeared on Facebook, impersonating Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa to post content and run advertisements for promotional programs with the intention of scamming and stealing customers\' money through fraudulent deposit transfers.<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udea8 We would like to officially announce that we have ONLY ONE OFFICIAL FANPAGE on Facebook at the following link:<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udc49 https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/BotonBlueHotelandSpa<\\/p><p>Please join us in reporting the following FAKE PAGES to prevent any unfortunate incidents:<\\/p><p>1\\/ https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/WelcomBotonBlueHotelSpa<\\/p><p>2\\/ https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/BotonBluelHotelSpa<\\/p><p>\\u26a0\\ufe0f IMPORTANT: Please be cautious when making any payments. Do NOT transfer money to personal bank accounts.<\\/p><p>To protect your rights and interests, please only follow and contact us through the following official channels:<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Official Fanpage: https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/BotonBlueHotelandSpa<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Official Website: https:\\/\\/botonblue.com<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Hotel Hotline: 0258 3836 868<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Sales Department Hotline: 0889 499 898<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc F&amp;B Department Hotline: 0889 559 090<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Hotel Email: info@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\udccc Sales Department Emails:<\\/p><p>reservation@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>sales@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>sales2@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>sales3@botonblue.com<\\/p><p>\\u26a0\\ufe0f Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa uses ONLY ONE OFFICIAL BANK ACCOUNT with the following details:<\\/p><p>Account Name: C\\u00d4NG TY TNHH KINH DOANH XU\\u1ea4T NH\\u1eacP KH\\u1ea8U VI\\u1ec6T D\\u01af\\u01a0NG<\\/p><p>Bank Name: Military Commercial Joint Stock Bank (MB Bank), Khanh Hoa Branch<\\/p><p>Account Number: 8011100183006 (VND)<\\/p><p>\\u26a0\\ufe0f All communication and promotional programs are only published through our official channels. The hotel is not responsible for any transactions or misleading information from fake fanpages.<\\/p><p>If you discover any suspicious fanpages, please inform us immediately so we can take prompt action.<\\/p><p>\\ud83d\\ude4f Thank you for your trust and support!<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/warning-multiple-fake-fanpages\\/sdsd.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/warning-multiple-fake-fanpages\\/artboard-1-copy.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/warning-multiple-fake-fanpages\\/artboard-1-1.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"status\":\"published\",\"image\":\"news\\/warning-multiple-fake-fanpages\\/artboard-1-copy.png\",\"tag\":null}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '171.243.63.154', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 11, 'WARNING: FAKE FANPAGES IMPERSONATING BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA', 'info', '2026-03-17 02:01:43', '2026-03-17 02:01:43'),
(378, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"c AT BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA 2024 \\ud83c\\udf84\\u2728\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"christmas-eve-buffet-at-boton-blue-hotel-spa-2024\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Take a look back at the unforgettable moments of Christmas Eve at Boton Blue Hotel & Spa, where the splendid ambiance blends perfectly with exquisite cuisine.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>CHRISTMAS EVE BUFFET AT BOTON BLUE HOTEL &amp; SPA 2024 \\ud83c\\udf84\\u2728<\\/p><p>Take a look back at the unforgettable moments of Christmas Eve at Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa, where the splendid ambiance blends perfectly with exquisite cuisine.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udf1f Festive Atmosphere: Every corner of the hotel was adorned with sparkling, warm decorations, creating a perfect Christmas vibe.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udf7d\\ufe0f Diverse Menu: Over 50 delightful dishes ranging from fresh seafood and BBQ to traditional Christmas classics like roasted turkey and yule log cake, all meticulously prepared.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udfb6 Exciting Music Program: Christmas melodies, Santa Claus, and surprising gifts lit up the evening.<\\/p><p>We sincerely thank all our guests for celebrating the season with Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa. See you at our upcoming special events!<\\/p><p>Wishing you and your family a peaceful Christmas and a prosperous New Year! \\ud83d\\udc96<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1777-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1766-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1853-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1771-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1868-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1860-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1848-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1840-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1814-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1807-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1804-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1802-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1800-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1796-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1795-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1794-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1790-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1784-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1781-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1778-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"status\":\"published\",\"image\":\"news\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\/img-1853-min.jpeg\",\"tag\":null}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '171.243.63.154', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 12, 'c AT BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA 2024 🎄✨', 'info', '2026-03-17 02:06:31', '2026-03-17 02:06:31'),
(379, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"CHRISTMAS EVE BUFFET AT BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA 2024 \\ud83c\\udf84\\u2728\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"christmas-eve-buffet-at-boton-blue-hotel-spa-2024\",\"slug_id\":\"89\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Take a look back at the unforgettable moments of Christmas Eve at Boton Blue Hotel & Spa, where the splendid ambiance blends perfectly with exquisite cuisine.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>CHRISTMAS EVE BUFFET AT BOTON BLUE HOTEL &amp; SPA 2024 \\ud83c\\udf84\\u2728<\\/p><p>Take a look back at the unforgettable moments of Christmas Eve at Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa, where the splendid ambiance blends perfectly with exquisite cuisine.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udf1f Festive Atmosphere: Every corner of the hotel was adorned with sparkling, warm decorations, creating a perfect Christmas vibe.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udf7d\\ufe0f Diverse Menu: Over 50 delightful dishes ranging from fresh seafood and BBQ to traditional Christmas classics like roasted turkey and yule log cake, all meticulously prepared.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udfb6 Exciting Music Program: Christmas melodies, Santa Claus, and surprising gifts lit up the evening.<\\/p><p>We sincerely thank all our guests for celebrating the season with Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa. See you at our upcoming special events!<\\/p><p>Wishing you and your family a peaceful Christmas and a prosperous New Year! \\ud83d\\udc96<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1777-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1766-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1853-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1771-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1868-min.jpeg\\