(380, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"CHRISTMAS EVE BUFFET AT BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA 2024 \\ud83c\\udf84\\u2728\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"christmas-eve-buffet-at-boton-blue-hotel-spa-2024\",\"slug_id\":\"89\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Take a look back at the unforgettable moments of Christmas Eve at Boton Blue Hotel & Spa, where the splendid ambiance blends perfectly with exquisite cuisine.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>CHRISTMAS EVE BUFFET AT BOTON BLUE HOTEL &amp; SPA 2024 \\ud83c\\udf84\\u2728<\\/p><p>Take a look back at the unforgettable moments of Christmas Eve at Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa, where the splendid ambiance blends perfectly with exquisite cuisine.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udf1f Festive Atmosphere: Every corner of the hotel was adorned with sparkling, warm decorations, creating a perfect Christmas vibe.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udf7d\\ufe0f Diverse Menu: Over 50 delightful dishes ranging from fresh seafood and BBQ to traditional Christmas classics like roasted turkey and yule log cake, all meticulously prepared.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udfb6 Exciting Music Program: Christmas melodies, Santa Claus, and surprising gifts lit up the evening.<\\/p><p>We sincerely thank all our guests for celebrating the season with Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa. See you at our upcoming special events!<\\/p><p>Wishing you and your family a peaceful Christmas and a prosperous New Year! \\ud83d\\udc96<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1777-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1766-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1853-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1771-min.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\\\\\/christmas-eve-buffet\\\\\\/img-1868-min.jpeg\\