(382, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"The festive atmosphere has filled every corner of Boton Blue Hotel & Spa\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"the-festive-atmosphere-has-filled-every-corner-of-boton-blue-hotel-spa\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"\\ud83c\\udf84\\u2728Christmas is coming\\u2026. The festive atmosphere has filled every corner of Boton Blue Hotel & Spa as another joyful Christmas season arrives.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>\\ud83c\\udf84\\u2728Christmas is coming\\u2026.<\\/p><p>The festive atmosphere has filled every corner of Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa as another joyful Christmas season arrives.<\\/p><p>\\ud83c\\udf32 In the main lobby, a beautifully adorned Christmas tree sparkles with radiant lights and vibrant gift boxes. Meticulously designed and elegant check-in spots promise to deliver stunning photos full of Christmas spirit.<\\/p><p>Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa is ready to welcome you to experience a Christmas season brimming with joy, warmth, and peace!<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-festive\\/img-1602.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-festive\\/img-1593.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-festive\\/img-1627.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-festive\\/img-1609.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-festive\\/img-1607.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"status\":\"published\",\"image\":\"news\\/the-festive\\/img-1627.jpeg\",\"tag\":null}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '171.243.63.154', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 13, 'The festive atmosphere has filled every corner of Boton Blue Hotel & Spa', 'info', '2026-03-17 02:22:26', '2026-03-17 02:22:26'),
(383, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"\\ud83c\\udf84 THE MAGICAL MOMENT OF LIGHTING THE CHRISTMAS TREE AT BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"the-magical-moment-of-lighting-the-christmas-tree-at-boton-blue-hotel-spa\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Last night, the \\\"The Christmas Tree Lighting Ceremony\\u201d at Boton Blue Hotel & Spa took place with the participation of valued guests and hotel staffs. The ceremony officially kicked off this year-end holiday season.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>\\ud83c\\udf84 THE MAGICAL MOMENT OF LIGHTING THE CHRISTMAS TREE AT BOTON BLUE HOTEL &amp; SPA<\\/p><p>Last night, the \\\"The Christmas Tree Lighting Ceremony\\u201d at Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa took place with the participation of valued guests and hotel staffs. The ceremony officially kicked off this year-end holiday season.<\\/p><p>Let\'s look back at the impressive moments from \\\"Christmas Tree Lighting ceremony\\u201d.<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1741.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1739.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1738.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1733.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1698.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1688.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1662.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1649.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1648.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/the-magical-moment\\/img-1642.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{