(409, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"WELCOME FAM TRIP OF KAZAKHSTAN TO BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"welcome-fam-trip-of-kazakhstan-to-boton-blue-hotel-spa\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Last week, Boton Blue Hotel & Spa had the privilege of hosting over 27 sales agents from Kazakhstan Astana and 25 sales agents from Kazakhstan Almaty.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p>WELCOME FAM TRIP OF KAZAKHSTAN TO BOTON BLUE HOTEL &amp; SPA<\\/p><p>Last week, Boton Blue Hotel &amp; Spa had the privilege of hosting over 27 sales agents from Kazakhstan Astana and 25 sales agents from Kazakhstan Almaty. They were here to assess our services at our hotel as part of their visit and business activities during the Nha Trang tourism survey, which Pegas Touristik organized.<\\/p><p>We anticipate that this visit to Nha Trang by the delegation will serve as a valuable opportunity to expand our connections, foster enduring partnerships between our two nations, and contribute to the growth of tourism in Nha Trang in the future.<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/fam-trip\\/img-0995.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/fam-trip\\/img-0991.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/fam-trip\\/img-0982.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"news\\/fam-trip\\/img-0976.jpeg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"status\":\"published\",\"image\":\"news\\/fam-trip\\/img-0991.jpeg\",\"tag\":null}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '171.243.63.154', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 15, 'WELCOME FAM TRIP OF KAZAKHSTAN TO BOTON BLUE HOTEL & SPA', 'info', '2026-03-17 03:22:35', '2026-03-17 03:22:35');

