nu/28.jpg\" alt=\"28.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/29.jpg\" alt=\"29.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/30.jpg\" alt=\"30.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/31.jpg\" alt=\"31.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/32.jpg\" alt=\"32.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/33.jpg\" alt=\"33.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/34.jpg\" alt=\"34.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/35.jpg\" alt=\"35.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/36.jpg\" alt=\"36.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/37.jpg\" alt=\"37.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/38.jpg\" alt=\"38.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/39.jpg\" alt=\"39.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/40.jpg\" alt=\"40.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/41.jpg\" alt=\"41.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/42.jpg\" alt=\"42.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/43.jpg\" alt=\"43.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/44.jpg\" alt=\"44.jpg\"> <img src=\"https://botonbluehotel.vt360.vn/storage/dinning/guangdong-restaurant/menu/45.jpg\" alt=\"45.jpg\"></div><p><button class=\"gd-next\">❯</button></p></div><div class=\"gd-menu-text\"><p>Enjoy fine Chinese cuisine at Guangdong Restaurant while soaking in the breathtaking view of the bay. With its interior adorned with black-red background décor and traditional lanterns, Guangdong Restaurant creates an immersive atmosphere complementing our elegant cuisine.</p><p class=\"gd-time\">Daily 4:30 PM - 10:00 PM</p></div></div><p><a class=\"gd-reservation-bar\" href=\"/reservation\"><span>MAKE A RESERVATION</span> &nbsp;</a></p></section>', 1, NULL, 'full-width', '', 'published', '2026-03-15 19:08:59', '2026-03-16 04:25:35');

